{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"2. **Wrong config key for scripts** — The handler checked `Config[\"command\"]` but the DSL stores script commands under `Config[\"run\"]`. Changed to check `Config[\"run\"]`.","timestamp":"2026-03-09T15:14:17.583728161Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","timestamp":"2026-03-09T15:14:17.583736457Z"}
